        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for information on cave rat.</p>
            <p>CD is obliged for news of J. D. Dana’s recovery.</p> 
<p>Will use BS’s information about cave rat in revised [3d] edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
